          </div>
          <div>
            <label class="text-gray-400 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider block mb-1.5">¿Cuántos kiosks necesitas?</label>
            <select class="w-full bg-gray-800 border border-white/5 focus:border-blue-500/50 rounded-xl p-3 text-sm text-white outline-none transition-colors">
              <option value="">Selecciona…</option>
